  "detailed_description": "<br><br><strong>EXCITING PARTY GAME</strong><br>In this local multiplayer game, sneak into the shadows and try to discretely eliminate your friends with your pickaxe, all in multiple arenas and game modes for up to 4 players. Use the Remote Play Together to play with your friends online !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/a361275c9856ee2fda01737f6d829631.poster.avif?t=1714166523\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/a361275c9856ee2fda01737f6d829631.webm?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/a361275c9856ee2fda01737f6d829631.mp4?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>PLAYABILITY ACCESSIBLE TO EVERYONE</strong><br>Sneaky Seekers is a game that's easy to get to grips with, and accessible to the whole family. Although the controls are simple, it's up to you to devise strategies, revealing your presence to everyone, or hiding and waiting for the right moment to strike. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/b9bd2819c161fc57e8bf7468567a2577.poster.avif?t=1714166523\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/b9bd2819c161fc57e8bf7468567a2577.webm?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/b9bd2819c161fc57e8bf7468567a2577.mp4?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SEVERAL GAME MODES & MODIFIERS</strong><br>From <i>Free For All</i> to <i>Team Fights</i>, have fun exploring the multiple game modes available. Each game mode comes with its own maps, and its enemies! Add modifiers for even more chaos!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/3e063d6902cbdcafc335284ddc130d9a.poster.avif?t=1714166523\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/3e063d6902cbdcafc335284ddc130d9a.webm?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/3e063d6902cbdcafc335284ddc130d9a.mp4?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<br><br><strong>EXCITING PARTY GAME</strong><br>In this local multiplayer game, sneak into the shadows and try to discretely eliminate your friends with your pickaxe, all in multiple arenas and game modes for up to 4 players. Use the Remote Play Together to play with your friends online !<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/a361275c9856ee2fda01737f6d829631.poster.avif?t=1714166523\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/a361275c9856ee2fda01737f6d829631.webm?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/a361275c9856ee2fda01737f6d829631.mp4?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>PLAYABILITY ACCESSIBLE TO EVERYONE</strong><br>Sneaky Seekers is a game that's easy to get to grips with, and accessible to the whole family. Although the controls are simple, it's up to you to devise strategies, revealing your presence to everyone, or hiding and waiting for the right moment to strike. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/b9bd2819c161fc57e8bf7468567a2577.poster.avif?t=1714166523\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/b9bd2819c161fc57e8bf7468567a2577.webm?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/b9bd2819c161fc57e8bf7468567a2577.mp4?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>SEVERAL GAME MODES & MODIFIERS</strong><br>From <i>Free For All</i> to <i>Team Fights</i>, have fun exploring the multiple game modes available. Each game mode comes with its own maps, and its enemies! Add modifiers for even more chaos!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/3e063d6902cbdcafc335284ddc130d9a.poster.avif?t=1714166523\" width=614 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/3e063d6902cbdcafc335284ddc130d9a.webm?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2459850/extras/3e063d6902cbdcafc335284ddc130d9a.mp4?t=1714166523\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
